1
00:01:07,800 --> 00:01:10,080
All the sorrows between you and me.

2
00:01:22,320 --> 00:01:22,850
Get them!

3
00:01:25,360 --> 00:01:27,400
How dare you impersonate Miss Su!

4
00:01:27,680 --> 00:01:28,680
Do you want to die?

5
00:01:28,720 --> 00:01:29,780
Don't hurt Miss Su.

6
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:31,160
Don't hurt Miss Su.

7
00:01:39,640 --> 00:01:40,370
Let go of her.

8
00:01:44,640 --> 00:01:45,240
Or else,

9
00:01:46,240 --> 00:01:47,100
you'll die too.

10
00:01:51,880 --> 00:01:52,740
Don't hurt her.

11
00:01:53,560 --> 00:01:54,920
It's a misunderstanding.

12
00:01:54,920 --> 00:01:56,380
Just a misunderstanding.

13
00:01:56,720 --> 00:01:57,920
She wants to kill you.

14
00:01:58,039 --> 00:01:59,570
And you're protecting her?

15
00:02:00,880 --> 00:02:02,160
It's all a misunderstanding.

16
00:02:02,160 --> 00:02:03,360
A misunderstanding.

17
00:02:06,160 --> 00:02:09,720
Then why did Lord Jian call her Miss Su just now?

18
00:02:10,479 --> 00:02:11,540
What did that mean?

19
00:02:16,600 --> 00:02:19,720
Ruilang, this person is a distant relative of mine.

20
00:02:20,560 --> 00:02:23,820
She brought her brothers today to help us catch Zhou Tiger.

21
00:02:27,760 --> 00:02:29,890
Lord Fang has such a distant relative?

22
00:02:30,760 --> 00:02:32,020
How come I didn't know?

23
00:02:34,200 --> 00:02:37,480
But when did Lord Fang develop a taste for such clothes?

24
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:41,960
Young Marquis, what Brother Fang said is true.

25
00:02:42,079 --> 00:02:44,480
He will explain the details to you later.

26
00:02:45,120 --> 00:02:46,440
Our most important task right now

27
00:02:46,440 --> 00:02:48,240
is to hurry and catch Zhou Tiger.

28
00:02:48,600 --> 00:02:48,920
I suspect she is Zhou Tiger.

29
00:02:48,920 --> 00:02:50,960
I suspect she is Zhou Tiger.

30
00:02:52,920 --> 00:02:53,780
Everyone knows

31
00:02:54,079 --> 00:02:56,800
that Zhou Tiger is a notorious bandit in the Jianghu.

32
00:02:56,800 --> 00:02:58,720
How does she resemble him at all?

33
00:02:59,440 --> 00:03:01,500
Young Marquis, Zhou Tiger is nearby.

34
00:03:01,680 --> 00:03:03,340
It's not too late to catch him.

35
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:05,400
Pihu.

36
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:06,400
Here.

37
00:03:06,760 --> 00:03:09,220
Take some men and search the area carefully.

38
00:03:10,400 --> 00:03:10,930
Yes, sir.

39
00:03:11,840 --> 00:03:12,440
Follow me.

40
00:03:19,320 --> 00:03:21,450
Don't worry. Zhou Tiger can't escape.

41
00:03:23,240 --> 00:03:24,570
Let's go back together.

42
00:03:25,600 --> 00:03:26,000
Wait.

43
00:03:28,040 --> 00:03:30,520
I really hit it off with this young lady.

44
00:03:31,079 --> 00:03:33,280
I'd like to have a private word with her.

45
00:03:44,320 --> 00:03:44,920
This time,

46
00:03:45,079 --> 00:03:47,440
we rescued you from the Dragon Shadow Guards.

47
00:03:47,440 --> 00:03:48,900
You should believe us now.

48
00:03:49,840 --> 00:03:50,840
Not necessarily.

49
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:54,860
Sister Song, you used to love wearing purplish red.

50
00:03:54,960 --> 00:03:56,400
Although you have a bold personality,

51
00:03:56,400 --> 00:03:58,079
you loved wearing flower hairpins.

52
00:03:58,079 --> 00:03:59,960
Especially the sword in your hand.

53
00:03:59,960 --> 00:04:01,490
I recognized it at a glance.

54
00:04:02,760 --> 00:04:04,680
My father treasured it for years.

55
00:04:05,320 --> 00:04:06,560
Because he trusted you,

56
00:04:06,560 --> 00:04:08,490
he gave it to you for self-defense.

57
00:04:09,480 --> 00:04:10,080
Am I right?

58
00:04:12,720 --> 00:04:14,380
If you still don't believe me,

59
00:04:14,440 --> 00:04:16,399
why not come back to the relay station with me?

60
00:04:16,399 --> 00:04:17,660
My sister is there too.

61
00:04:18,519 --> 00:04:20,920
We couldn't possibly find two look-alikes

62
00:04:21,240 --> 00:04:23,300
to pretend to be Lord Su's daughters.

63
00:04:25,560 --> 00:04:26,690
Is Yan'er there too?

64
00:04:26,960 --> 00:04:27,360
Yes.

65
00:04:35,480 --> 00:04:37,040
Sister, you're back.

66
00:04:37,040 --> 00:04:38,840
Yan'er, this is...

67
00:04:40,720 --> 00:04:42,800
You must be Yan'er.

68
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:44,460
Who are you?

69
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:50,000
Don't be afraid, Yan'er.

70
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:51,400
This is a friend of Father's.

71
00:04:51,400 --> 00:04:53,060
We met her when we were little.

72
00:04:53,280 --> 00:04:53,680
She...

73
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:56,400
She just wanted to confirm our identities.

74
00:04:58,480 --> 00:04:59,159
Wonderful.

75
00:04:59,960 --> 00:05:02,360
Lord Su's children are still alive.

76
00:05:03,320 --> 00:05:04,520
In the blink of an eye,

77
00:05:06,160 --> 00:05:07,290
you've all grown up.

78
00:05:11,360 --> 00:05:11,920
Sister.

79
00:05:12,840 --> 00:05:15,360
Do you know this brand marks me as an official prostitute?

80
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:16,820
Every time it is revealed,

81
00:05:16,880 --> 00:05:18,320
it pierces my heart.

82
00:05:19,400 --> 00:05:20,280
I'm sorry, Yan'er.

83
00:05:20,280 --> 00:05:20,740
Yan'er.

84
00:05:21,120 --> 00:05:21,580
Yan'er.

85
00:05:24,040 --> 00:05:24,840
Wait a moment.

86
00:05:25,080 --> 00:05:26,210
I'll go comfort her.

87
00:05:30,560 --> 00:05:32,159
I have something to tell you.

88
00:05:32,360 --> 00:05:34,490
It'll be hard to talk when they return.

89
00:05:35,080 --> 00:05:37,120
Take me somewhere private first.

90
00:05:39,680 --> 00:05:40,080
Okay.

91
00:05:47,080 --> 00:05:47,480
Come.

92
00:05:59,120 --> 00:06:01,120
Sister, what is this urgent matter?

93
00:06:04,280 --> 00:06:07,080
Back then, Lord Su knew he was in grave danger.

94
00:06:07,640 --> 00:06:10,840
So he came to Jinzhou under the guise of ancestor worship,

95
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:17,460
to hide the evidence he found in a safe place.

96
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:23,330
Lord Su had also long predicted

97
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:26,680
that he would be framed as the scapegoat for the witchcraft case.

98
00:06:26,680 --> 00:06:29,080
I'm glad you weren't implicated back then.

99
00:06:30,520 --> 00:06:31,200
But Sister,

100
00:06:31,400 --> 00:06:34,460
why didn't you hand the evidence directly to Lord Jian?

101
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:39,600
Lord Su gave his life for these things.

102
00:06:40,159 --> 00:06:41,560
I was extremely careful.

103
00:06:42,280 --> 00:06:43,080
But back then,

104
00:06:43,520 --> 00:06:45,050
I didn't trust Jian Boning.

105
00:06:45,400 --> 00:06:46,520
After Lord Su died,

106
00:06:46,760 --> 00:06:48,320
he turned to serve the enemy,

107
00:06:48,320 --> 00:06:49,920
joining Qin Heng's faction.

108
00:06:50,360 --> 00:06:51,800
But now it's clear.

109
00:06:52,320 --> 00:06:53,159
Back then,

110
00:06:53,440 --> 00:06:55,000
he was enduring humiliation for the greater good.

111
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:56,400
He didn't betray Lord Su.

112
00:06:56,840 --> 00:06:58,200
But at the time,

113
00:06:58,560 --> 00:07:00,440
I had to be on my guard.

114
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:05,890
Thank you, Sister Song.

115
00:07:06,520 --> 00:07:09,040
It's been hard on you these years.

116
00:07:17,040 --> 00:07:17,880
By the way,

117
00:07:18,560 --> 00:07:21,920
the ones who massacred the Su Manor were experts from the Imperial Palace.

118
00:07:21,920 --> 00:07:23,880
How did you escape?

119
00:07:30,360 --> 00:07:31,420
Because of Yan'er.

120
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:39,560
When the incident happened to my family,

121
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:42,850
it was late into the night that day,

122
00:07:43,240 --> 00:07:46,640
and Father still hadn't come to tell Yan'er and me to go to bed.

123
00:07:46,640 --> 00:07:50,000
So Yan'er suggested we play hide-and-seek.

124
00:07:53,040 --> 00:07:54,440
Two wooden sticks.

125
00:07:55,520 --> 00:07:58,000
One long, one short.

126
00:07:59,200 --> 00:08:01,800
The one with the long stick would be the seeker.

127
00:08:02,640 --> 00:08:04,840
The short one hides.

128
00:08:06,640 --> 00:08:08,440
I actually got the long one.

129
00:08:09,840 --> 00:08:12,040
But I was really sleepy that day.

130
00:08:12,040 --> 00:08:13,570
I didn't want to run around.

131
00:08:15,240 --> 00:08:16,560
So I took my stick

132
00:08:17,960 --> 00:08:19,520
and snapped it in half.

133
00:08:21,520 --> 00:08:22,440
So,

134
00:08:24,600 --> 00:08:26,160
I became the one hiding.

135
00:08:27,560 --> 00:08:30,220
I should have been the one taken to Qihong Tower,

136
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:32,880
not Yan'er.

137
00:08:40,640 --> 00:08:41,520
All right.

138
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:44,090
It's all in the past.

139
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:46,090
It's all in the past.

140
00:08:48,480 --> 00:08:50,210
Lord Su is watching from above.

141
00:08:50,280 --> 00:08:51,940
Yan'er has escaped, at least.

142
00:08:56,320 --> 00:08:57,600
When Jian Boning returns,

143
00:08:57,600 --> 00:08:59,330
I will get the evidence from him

144
00:08:59,360 --> 00:09:01,160
to clear the Su family's name.

145
00:09:01,640 --> 00:09:02,700
Let's go together.

146
00:09:02,720 --> 00:09:04,050
No, it's too dangerous.

147
00:09:04,360 --> 00:09:05,480
If anything were to happen,

148
00:09:05,480 --> 00:09:06,960
how could we face Lord Su?

149
00:09:07,240 --> 00:09:08,200
This is my family's business.

150
00:09:08,200 --> 00:09:08,520
Stop talking.

151
00:09:08,520 --> 00:09:09,280
How could I...

152
00:09:09,280 --> 00:09:10,280
It's decided.

153
00:09:16,960 --> 00:09:18,920
Take this knockout powder.

154
00:09:19,880 --> 00:09:21,480
I spent years developing it.

155
00:09:21,480 --> 00:09:22,960
If you encounter any danger,

156
00:09:22,960 --> 00:09:24,620
you can use it in an emergency.

157
00:09:24,640 --> 00:09:26,440
It knocks people out instantly.

158
00:09:27,440 --> 00:09:28,480
But...

159
00:09:29,520 --> 00:09:31,600
But the effect

160
00:09:32,280 --> 00:09:34,760
doesn't seem to last very long.

161
00:09:34,880 --> 00:09:36,840
Run as soon as you use it.

162
00:09:38,920 --> 00:09:39,720
Okay.

163
00:09:40,160 --> 00:09:40,960
I'll take it.

164
00:09:50,480 --> 00:09:53,720
When the time comes, we'll go from this point to this point,

165
00:09:53,720 --> 00:09:54,980
and then to this point.

166
00:09:56,880 --> 00:09:59,280
Then how do we get past this point?

167
00:10:00,640 --> 00:10:02,840
You are more familiar with this mountain.

168
00:10:02,840 --> 00:10:03,520
Mm-hmm.

169
00:10:03,800 --> 00:10:04,440
Okay.

170
00:10:04,640 --> 00:10:06,640
I'll handle the planning then.

171
00:10:24,440 --> 00:10:25,800
Why are you sneaking around here

172
00:10:25,800 --> 00:10:27,120
and eavesdropping on them?

173
00:10:27,120 --> 00:10:27,680
I am not.

174
00:10:28,200 --> 00:10:31,000
I was just checking if they were done talking.

175
00:10:31,040 --> 00:10:32,900
Yan'er is waiting for them to eat.

176
00:10:34,240 --> 00:10:36,770
Your sister was crying her heart out just now.

177
00:10:36,800 --> 00:10:38,600
Is she in the mood to cook?

178
00:10:39,840 --> 00:10:42,200
Are you and Fangji keeping something from me?

179
00:10:42,200 --> 00:10:43,160
Of course not.

180
00:10:44,040 --> 00:10:47,440
What could possibly escape your sharp eyes, Little Marquis?

181
00:10:48,960 --> 00:10:50,020
Then let me ask you,

182
00:10:50,560 --> 00:10:53,490
what did you talk about the day you drank with Fangji?

183
00:10:53,640 --> 00:10:55,970
And how did you end up sleeping in his room?

184
00:10:56,960 --> 00:10:59,560
He just wanted to thank me that day,

185
00:10:59,760 --> 00:11:01,220
so he treated me to a drink.

186
00:11:03,360 --> 00:11:04,220
What about you?

187
00:11:05,320 --> 00:11:07,120
Are you hiding anything from me?

188
00:11:08,920 --> 00:11:11,240
Little Marquis, I really have something urgent today.

189
00:11:11,240 --> 00:11:12,900
Let's talk another day, okay?

190
00:11:13,400 --> 00:11:14,200
I'm going now.

191
00:11:14,800 --> 00:11:15,840
Talk later.

192
00:11:35,200 --> 00:11:36,240
Fangji.

193
00:11:36,960 --> 00:11:38,000
What's wrong?

194
00:11:38,000 --> 00:11:39,160
Why the rush?

195
00:11:39,760 --> 00:11:40,840
I just heard

196
00:11:41,200 --> 00:11:42,640
Sister Song and Lord Jian

197
00:11:42,960 --> 00:11:45,090
are going to get the evidence tonight.

198
00:11:46,720 --> 00:11:48,120
Come with me, okay?

199
00:11:50,280 --> 00:11:51,080
Okay.

200
00:11:52,480 --> 00:11:53,340
Sit down first.

201
00:11:57,160 --> 00:11:59,280
I roasted these chestnuts for you myself.

202
00:11:59,280 --> 00:12:00,680
Taste it.

203
00:12:01,880 --> 00:12:03,680
You know how to roast chestnuts?

204
00:12:04,440 --> 00:12:05,400
Impressive.

205
00:12:09,200 --> 00:12:10,240
Is it good?

206
00:12:10,240 --> 00:12:11,170
It's delicious.

207
00:12:11,240 --> 00:12:13,120
I have something important to tell you.

208
00:12:13,120 --> 00:12:13,920
Wait a moment.

209
00:12:14,680 --> 00:12:15,080
Okay.

210
00:12:25,560 --> 00:12:26,640
What is going on?

211
00:12:27,480 --> 00:12:28,480
Why so secretive?

212
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:51,660
Yan'er pays her respects to you, Young Marquis.

213
00:12:52,760 --> 00:12:54,090
You were looking for me?

214
00:12:55,360 --> 00:12:56,960
I want to cooperate with you.

215
00:13:06,200 --> 00:13:08,200
I want to marry into the Fang family.

216
00:13:08,560 --> 00:13:10,000
And you want my sister.

217
00:13:10,600 --> 00:13:11,930
We each get what we want.

218
00:13:18,240 --> 00:13:19,000
What?

219
00:13:19,440 --> 00:13:20,800
Am I wrong?

220
00:13:21,840 --> 00:13:24,080
Don't you want to be with my sister?

221
00:13:30,760 --> 00:13:32,600
You'd better behave yourself.

222
00:13:33,440 --> 00:13:35,900
If you dare hurt a hair on your sister's head,

223
00:13:36,800 --> 00:13:38,200
I won't spare you.

224
00:13:49,400 --> 00:13:50,720
He's not back yet.

225
00:14:02,040 --> 00:14:05,360
Fang Ji, did you lock the door?

226
00:14:05,480 --> 00:14:06,960
I can't open it.

227
00:14:07,200 --> 00:14:08,400
Did you lock it?

228
00:14:08,800 --> 00:14:09,920
Open the door!

229
00:14:10,720 --> 00:14:11,520
Fang Ji.

230
00:14:13,200 --> 00:14:14,460
Fang Ji, open the door!

231
00:14:15,760 --> 00:14:17,280
Fang Ji, open this door!

232
00:14:18,520 --> 00:14:20,520
What are you doing, Fang Ji?

233
00:14:21,760 --> 00:14:23,160
I just saw Jian Boning.

234
00:14:24,000 --> 00:14:24,840
Don't worry.

235
00:14:25,320 --> 00:14:27,180
They will retrieve the evidence.

236
00:14:27,360 --> 00:14:29,880
This concerns the wrongful conviction of my father and my entire family.

237
00:14:29,880 --> 00:14:31,160
I have to go myself.

238
00:14:31,920 --> 00:14:32,720
You know that.

239
00:14:33,040 --> 00:14:33,960
I must find out

240
00:14:33,960 --> 00:14:35,400
what the connection is between the Wugu case back then

241
00:14:35,400 --> 00:14:36,660
and this current case.

242
00:14:36,720 --> 00:14:38,680
I also need to know who is pulling the strings.

243
00:14:38,680 --> 00:14:41,080
Nothing is more important than your safety.

244
00:14:41,080 --> 00:14:43,680
Do you have any idea how important this is to me?

245
00:14:43,760 --> 00:14:46,000
Do you know how long I've waited for this day?

246
00:14:46,000 --> 00:14:47,440
Why are you doing this?

247
00:14:47,840 --> 00:14:48,880
Fang Ji, open the door.

248
00:14:48,880 --> 00:14:49,880
Listen to me.

249
00:14:51,960 --> 00:14:54,360
You came with me to Jinzhou to investigate,

250
00:14:54,400 --> 00:14:56,860
and we've brought many suspects to justice.

251
00:14:58,840 --> 00:15:02,360
You are now a thorn in the side of many corrupt officials.

252
00:15:03,560 --> 00:15:05,960
It's safer for you to stay inside.

253
00:15:11,080 --> 00:15:12,880
Are you really not letting me go?

254
00:15:12,880 --> 00:15:13,680
No.

255
00:15:20,520 --> 00:15:21,320
Fine.

256
00:15:23,040 --> 00:15:23,840
I promise you.

257
00:15:24,480 --> 00:15:25,340
I won't go then.

258
00:15:30,360 --> 00:15:31,160
Go ahead.

259
00:15:33,600 --> 00:15:36,480
You have something important to tell me.

260
00:15:38,880 --> 00:15:39,840
Is this it?

261
00:15:56,480 --> 00:15:57,520
I wanted to say...

262
00:16:09,200 --> 00:16:12,160
A glance in the misty rain, a dream.
